[I] Kronosnet is a network abstraction layer

[T] Kronosnet, often referred to as knet, is a network abstraction layer designed for
[T] High Availability use cases, where redundancy, security, fault tolerance and fast
[T] fail-over are the core requirements of your application.

[U] https://kronosnet.org/

